\ About us \

Founded in 2017 by Qassim Al-Zaki, Chef Friend was born from a passion for bringing the finest Asian cooking ingredients—especially sushi essentials—to restaurants and retailers across Saudi Arabia and the GCC.

Our journey began with premium green tea, but we quickly recognized a growing market demand for high-quality, hard-to-find ingredients. This realization led to the development of our own brand, Chef Friend, dedicated to consistently providing top-tier ingredients to our valued customers.

Our Commitment to Excellence

Our Impact

We take pride in knowing that top restaurants rely on our premium ingredients to craft their signature dishes, driving us to maintain the highest standards in everything we do.

Our Culture

Innovation and growth are at the heart of Chef Friend. We are always looking ahead, developing new products that meet the ever-changing needs of the market.

Our mission is to inspire every chef to create unique
culinary experiences by providing high-quality
ingredients that support their creativity and excellence.
